r%E1%BA%A7n-t%C3%ACnh-bi%E1%BB%83u/poem-0BeSN4In5c5TT58DpTZQJQ">Lý Mật trần tình biểu - 李密陳情表</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/Thanh-H%C6%B0-%C4%91%E1%BB%99ng-k%C3%BD/poem-4T3tCDz0kElUt1cfxT71ww">Thanh Hư động ký - 清虛洞記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/author-3K5mDhkNpasGeB0z-64AmA">Nguyễn Phi Khanh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%C3%A1-Thu%E1%BA%A7n/T%E1%BB%91ng-L%C3%BD-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-T%C3%A2n-Ti%C3%AAu-Ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Nhai-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-vc2da7Ko4q1xrkGJ5lyPWg">Tống Lý Trọng Tân, Tiêu Phương Nhai tự - 送李仲賓蕭方崖序</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%C3%A1-Thu%E1%BA%A7n/author-cyxaXiD7wkE2as9RxMzt9Q">Trương Bá Thuần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%9Ac-V%C4%83n/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%C6%B0-th%E1%BB%A5-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-U_1Ea5w3Tq93blzoXUzU0Q">Tương tư thụ kỳ 3 - 相思樹其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%9Ac-V%C4%83n/author-xVo9muuF2eAhEr09snbNTQ">Úc Văn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Xu%C3%A2n-d%E1%BA%A1-li%C3%AAn-nga/poem-cLCb98Tc0rnGQzwe5orAYQ">Xuân dạ liên nga - 春夜憐蛾</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br></div>	</div>
